Package com.jakubpetriska.gameengine.api

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Messenger
    Allows sending messages out of the engine and receiving messages coming into the engine.
    Renderer
    Provides rendering functionality.
    Time
    Provides valuable information about time.
    TouchInput
    Provides access to application's touch input.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Application
    Provides important engine features.
    CollisionsSystem
    Detects collisions of colliders in the scene.
    Color
    Represents color.
    Component
    Represents GameObject's component.
    Debug
    Provides information about debug settings for the current application version and provides debugging functionality.
    Display
    Describes properties of device's display and provides convenience methods for working with these properties.
    GameObject
    Represents an object.
    MeshData
    Contains data about vertices, faces and normals of mesh.
    Primitives
    Lists names of available primitive meshes.
    Touch
    Container storing information about one currently running touch event in one particular frame.
